@startuml
title UC-01. Настроить мониторинг сервиса

actor "Специалист поддержки" as Support
participant "Monitoring API" as API
participant "Monitoring Config Module" as Config
database "Monitoring DB" as DB

Support -> API: POST /api/v1/services
API -> Config: createService(request)

Config -> Config: validate service data
Config -> Config: validate responsibles

Config -> DB: INSERT service
DB --> Config: service_id

loop for each responsible
    Config -> DB: INSERT responsible
    DB --> Config: responsible_id

    Config -> DB: INSERT service_responsible
    DB --> Config: relation saved
end

Config --> API: created service with responsibles
API --> Support: 201 Created + service_id

@enduml